  "source_file": "ngs_library_prep.ot2.apiv2.py",
  "intent_precise": "Lexogen QuantSeq 3`mRNA FWD NGS Library Prep: Using final output plate (load empty) (pcr_plate, slot 1), reagent tuberack with 1.5ml snapcap tubes (tuberack, slot 2), reagent reservoir (reservoir, slot 3), magplate (pcr_plate, slot 5). With magdeck_gen module, tempdeck_gen module. (1) Pause: Refill 20\u00b5l tipracks in slots 6 and 9 before resuming. (2) Pause: Refill 200\u00b5l tipracks in slots 8, 10, and 11 before resuming. (3) Transfer from source A1 to destination A1. (4) Pause: Place sample plate in cycler at 85C for 3 minutes, then cool down to 42C. Return sample plate to OT-2 when finished. (5) Pause: Place sample plate in cycler at 42C for 15 minutes. Return sample plate to OT-2 when finished. (6) Pause: Place sample plate in cycler at 95C for 10 minutes. Return sample plate to OT-2 when finished. (7) Pause: Place sample plate in cycler at 98C for 1 minute. Return sample plate to OT-2 when finished. (8) Pause: Place sample plate in cycler at 25C for 15 minutes. Return sample plate to OT-2 when finished. (9) Engage magnets for bead separation. (10) Incubate for 5 minutes. (11) Transfer 120\u00b5L from etoh (A1, 0) to destination (A1, A1). (12) Wait 30 seconds. (13) Transfer 130\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (14) Incubate for 10 minutes. (15) Disengage magnets to release beads. (16) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (17) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (18) Mix 5 times at 10\u00b5L. (19) Transfer 56\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (20) Mix 3 times at 10\u00b5L. (21) Incubate for 5 minutes. (22) Engage magnets for bead separation. (23) Incubate for 5 minutes. (24) Distribute 5\u00b5L from source A1 to destination wells A1, A1, A1. (25) Pause: Perform PCR cycling reaction, then place SP2 on the magnetic deck. (26) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (27) Mix 3 times at 10\u00b5L. (28) Incubate for 5 minutes. (29) Engage magnets for bead separation. (30) Incubate for 5 minutes. (31) Transfer 65\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (32) Disengage magnets to release beads. (33) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (34) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source to destination. (35) Mix 5 times at 10\u00b5L. (36) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (37) Mix 3 times at 10\u00b5L. (38) Incubate for 5 minutes. (39) Engage magnets for bead separation. (40) Incubate for 5 minutes. (41) Transfer 120\u00b5L from etoh (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1). (42) Wait 30 seconds. (43) Transfer 130\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (44) Incubate for 10 minutes. (45) Disengage magnets to release beads. (46) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (47) Mix 5 times at 10\u00b5L. (48) Engage magnets for bead separation. (49) Incubate for 5 minutes. (50) Transfer 15\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1, A1, A1, magnetic bead separation. (volumes 5\u00b5L-130\u00b5L, ~63 min total)",
  "intent": "Here's the Lexogen QuantSeq 3' mRNA FWD NGS Library Prep protocol - set up your OT-2 with an empty PCR plate in slot 1, tuberack in slot 2, reservoir in slot 3, and magplate in slot 5, making sure to refill your 20\u00b5l tipracks in slots 6 and 9 plus 200\u00b5l tipracks in slots 8, 10, and 11 before starting. You'll be doing several thermal cycling steps at specific temperatures (85\u00b0C for 3 minutes, cool to 42\u00b0C for 15 minutes, then 95\u00b0C for 10 minutes, 98\u00b0C for 1 minute, and finally 25\u00b0C for 15 minutes), followed by magnetic bead separations with various incubation times and reagent transfers including ethanol washes at 120\u00b5L and 130\u00b5L volumes. The protocol involves multiple mixing steps at 10\u00b5L volumes, bead capture and release cycles, and ends with PCR cycling before final cleanup steps with 30\u00b5L transfers and a final 15\u00b5L elution from A1 to A1. Remember to engage and disengage the magnets as specified for the 5-minute bead separation steps throughout the workflow.",
